    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within ±15% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence and documented engineering controls. The credibility assessment supports acceptance of the model for the stated COU.",
